content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1271.32 - Charges for use of terminal to be paid in cash; exceptions

State Regulations

All charges due for the use of the air terminal shall be
billed to the owner or operator of the aircraft using the terminal unless
payment is made to the airport operator in cash. Notes
